---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Clients — Adam Barnes | Web Design & Photography"
  description="Clients who’ve trusted Adam Barnes with web design, branding and photography — from arts consultants and festival organisers to property agencies and beyond."
  canonical="https://www.adambarnes.biz/clients.html"
  ogImage="https://www.adambarnes.biz/assets/og-clients.jpg"
  bodyClass="page-clients"
  active="clients"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "CollectionPage",
    "name": "Clients — Adam Barnes",
    "url": "https://www.adambarnes.biz/clients.html",
    "description": "A selection of the brands and businesses Adam Barnes has worked with across web design, branding and photography.",
    "creator": {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "Adam Barnes",
      "url": "https://www.adambarnes.biz"
    }
  }
  </script>
  </Fragment>

<main>
    <header class="section-header clients-header">
      <h1 class="section-title">
        <span>Inspired</span>
        <span class="accent">Clients</span>
        <span class="by-line">by Adam</span>
      </h1>
      <h2 class="intro-lead">From chocolatiers to fake blood to government.</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Businesses put their trust in me to not only answer their brief, but to take their brand to a new level. Most of my work comes from word of mouth. My clients’ voice is the heart of my marketing.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="clients-grid clients-grid--three" aria-label="Client testimonials">

      <!-- Brian Bush -->
      <article class="client-card reveal">
        <div class="client-avatar" aria-hidden="true">BB</div>
        <h3 class="client-name">Brian Bush</h3>
        <p class="client-company">Turning Factor</p>
        <p class="client-desc">Adam is simply one of the nicest people I have ever met. The fact that he is also brilliant at what he does and truly cares about it and his clients is testament to his amazing and hugely engaging personality. A stunningly talented photographer and digital genius. You simply would be getting absolute value should you engage him. I have now, as of 2026, worked with and known Adam as a close friend for 14 years and this will continue for a long while yet. He is my immediate go-to for everything he does.</p>
        <ul class="client-tags" aria-label="Services provided">
          <li>Web Design</li>
          <li>Photography</li>
          <li>Branding</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- First Light Festival -->
      <article class="client-card reveal">
        <div class="client-avatar" aria-hidden="true">FL</div>
        <h3 class="client-name">First Light Festival</h3>
        <p class="client-company">Lowestoft</p>
        <p class="client-desc">We’ve worked with Adam every year at First Light Festival since 2019. He’s become a trusted part of the team — always reliable, easy to work with, and consistently delivering images that capture the spirit of the event. He’s photographed everything from the festival beach at sunrise to backstage portraits and press calls, and always turns around fantastic results. When other organisations ask us for a photographer recommendation, Adam is always our first call.</p>
        <ul class="client-tags" aria-label="Services provided">
          <li>Photography</li>
          <li>Events</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="case-study-firstlight-festival.html" class="cs-card-link">View case study →</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Mark -->
      <article class="client-card reveal">
        <div class="client-avatar" aria-hidden="true">M</div>
        <h3 class="client-name">Mark</h3>
        <p class="client-company">Boat Hire Norwich</p>
        <p class="client-desc">I’m really pleased with everything and am excited for the coming season. The new and more structured start times, combined with the redesigned plugin, should make for a much smoother, easier-to-manage workflow. The custom plugin you created sounds very efficient.</p>
        <ul class="client-tags" aria-label="Services provided">
          <li>Web Design</li>
          <li>Coding</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="case-study-boat-hire-norwich.html" class="cs-card-link">View case study →</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Donna Dawson -->
      <article class="client-card reveal">
        <div class="client-avatar" aria-hidden="true">DD</div>
        <h3 class="client-name">Donna Dawson</h3>
        <p class="client-company">London</p>
        <p class="client-desc">I have worked with Adam for many years now on various projects. I quite literally wouldn’t work with anyone else when it comes to creating a new website and for photography work. Because not only is he super talented and enormously creative, he also has in-depth and extensive technical knowledge on his craft. Add that to being a top human that I trust implicitly and always delivers top quality work on time — why would you go anywhere else?</p>
        <ul class="client-tags" aria-label="Services provided">
          <li>Branding</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Matt Sykes -->
      <article class="client-card reveal">
        <div class="client-avatar" aria-hidden="true">MS</div>
        <h3 class="client-name">Matt Sykes</h3>
        <p class="client-company">Sales Cadence</p>
        <p class="client-desc">I’ve worked with Adam since launching my business back in 2015 and he’s been a constant source of website wisdom and creativity ever since. His knowledge of the industry is exceptional, he’s easy to work with, highly responsive, and he consistently brings practical ideas that improve my online presence.</p>
        <ul class="client-tags" aria-label="Services provided">
          <li>Web Design</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Tom Appleton -->
      <article class="client-card reveal">
        <div class="client-avatar" aria-hidden="true">TA</div>
        <h3 class="client-name">Tom Appleton</h3>
        <p class="client-company">Tom Appleton Arts</p>
        <p class="client-desc">Adam is the complete package. His knowledge, skills, and professionalism are a joy to work with. From branding concept and design, through to excellent photographic skills, website creation, and later website re-development done to reflect changing online search habits, Adam’s abilities, advice, and careful support of my brand is hugely appreciated. I wouldn’t go into battle without him.</p>
        <ul class="client-tags" aria-label="Services provided">
          <li>Branding</li>
          <li>Web Design</li>
          <li>Photography</li>
          <li>SEO</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="case-study-tom-appleton.html" class="cs-card-link">View case study →</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Jessie — Gardner Denley -->
      <article class="client-card reveal">
        <div class="client-avatar" aria-hidden="true">GD</div>
        <h3 class="client-name">Jessie</h3>
        <p class="client-company">Gardner Denley</p>
        <p class="client-desc">Working with Adam was a fantastic experience. He brought a perfect balance of creativity, technical expertise, and professionalism to the project, delivering a website that looks incredible and performs brilliantly. What really stood out was his ability to understand the niche placement of our business, our distinct vision and translate it into something even better than expected. The process felt smooth and collaborative throughout, and the end result speaks for itself. It would be an absolute pleasure to work with Adam again, and I have and will continue to highly recommend him to anyone looking to elevate their online presence.</p>
        <ul class="client-tags" aria-label="Services provided">
          <li>Web Design</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="case-study-gardner-denley.html" class="cs-card-link">View case study →</a>
      </article>

      <!-- CTA card -->
      <article class="client-card client-card--cta reveal">
        <p class="client-cta-text">Want to work together?</p>
        <p class="client-cta-support">These are the people who keep coming back. There’s room for you.</p>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-cta" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Get in touch</a>
      </article>

    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
